reviewText: Arrived on time. No issues with the seller. Not my favorite Billy Blanks DVD. Only used it a couple times and just couldn't get into it.

I have been doing Tae Bo since the 90's and these DVDs were challenging.  You can do the workouts without the amplifier, but it will definitely be more intense using one.  You can tell a huge difference.  Some of the moves do take a bit to get used with the equipment, but the results are definitely worth it!
